{"tid":45920,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手]我成為了一個不擇手段上位的教蓄","createTime":"2016-12-19T09:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T02:21:40.000Z","uid":35082,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0cfacfcc271d5e26adf571c5b08a457994718aa","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我叫吳德富。<br />\n10年前，我喺香港最著名嘅學府畢業，<br />\n間學校叫做香港大學&hellip;&hellip;.<br />\n<br />\n我叫以前間學校做香港大學都冇錯架，<br />\n只不過，要加返公開2個字姐!<br />\n全名叫香港公開大學先啱!<br />\n大家都喺港大,不用分得哪麼細！<br />\n<br />\n好可惜,出面嘅顧主絕對唔係咁諗。<br />\n「你讀公大架？」我每次見工都比人呢條問題。<br />\n「係&hellip;&hellip;」我心諗，履歷表都係寫撚咗，你問乜春？<br />\n講到底，咪又係班HR同顧主想恥笑我。<br />\n「讀OU真係好失禮你咩？正仆街！唔請我咪算囉，你班仆街食屎啦！」<br />\n正所謂百忍成金，為左搵工搵錢，當然我冇講出口啦。<br />\n「你返屋企等通知啦！」結果見完工都係得到同一個答覆。<br />\n<br />\n之後果一年，我乜工都做過。<br />\n地盤、地產、物流&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;你冇睇錯，大學生去做呢d工，<br />\n我只係差在未賣屎忽。<br />\n呢一年，絕對係我一生中ge低谷，受盡白眼。<br />\n點解讀完大學仲要做呢d辛苦工？點解呀！！！！<br />\n我覺得，我遲早會頂唔順。<br />\n「唔通我呢世都同個名一樣，唔得富？」<br />\n<br />\n「仔，不如試下做老師啦！」老母有日食飯突然同我咁講。<br />\n「點解&hellip;&hellip;？」<br />\n「人工又唔錯，都叫專業人士啦，你讀多張教育文憑實有人請！」<br />\n「唔止添呀，聽日講教band3學校做都唔洗做，日日hea就得。」老豆係隔離附和。<br />\n「er&hellip;&hellip;」我係個心到打量一陣，就決定去馬！<br />\n<br />\n我用一年時間讀完全日制PGDE之後，<br />\n好好彩比我返到以前間中學做。<br />\n點知&hellip;&hellip;係請我做教學助理！仲要得萬三人工！！！<br />\n代課係我做、文件係我打、連活動都要我帶。<br />\n其實我同一個雜工係冇任何分別，<br />\n只不過我多佢地一個大學位。<br />\n我明白，呢個社會一定係弱肉強食，自己一定要爭氣。<br />\n就係咁，我決定盡一切方法上位，令所有人睇得起我呢個OU仔！！！"},{"pid":"d07109203810a78f2300325fe22e4954407dd531","tid":45920,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"6827dfc96bc73c588b14d244d92389ee17f3ce73","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T09:55:41.000Z","msg":"新手寫故 唔好屌得咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c64296887873e00ee20e7f46ca7ec099dcafaf","tid":45920,"uid":9766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8064b99e18613808a6207a66cf8e389994563236","tid":45920,"uid":65562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:10:21.000Z","msg":"畜？"},{"pid":"bc7395d7d1a413d643b75aaed17080260e30080f","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畜？</blockquote><br />\n手快打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝指正"},{"pid":"a05932773c4570bbcd53c8803d9ca08e7c65002b","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:16:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a74efcad30d34aca7dfb3a1d9e73ea0c5c57f16b","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"垃圾故冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087cfc8761cbb537ba93ebdd7916c044ae81cf87","tid":45920,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:26:46.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"d33d66a8ea68c40875f424d28d5ffb3afe1a623d","tid":45920,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n評已正，期待下文，希望樓主加速出文<br />\n一句講哂：有文先有人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4f07dcef854c584f26997acf612ed5489ddce5","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n評已正，期待下文，希望樓主加速出文<br />\n一句講哂：有文先有人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇下有冇人睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38037a713550f299b99a15ab7e10503e9ad13555","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:03:49.000Z","msg":"我嘅目標係要4年內上到主任級，然後等到有朝一日上到更高位置！<br />\n<br />\n「呢條數你喺咪唔識計呀？我可以教你喎!」<br />\n每次代課我都會教啲學生做吓功課，目的唔係咁單純希望幫吓佢哋。<br />\n而係想同班學生打好關係，比佢哋知到我絕對有能力做全職老師。<br />\n就算校長巡堂，都唔會覺得我太hea，將來升職都快啲!<br />\n<br />\n「平日有功課唔識可唔可以問你架？」<br />\n「新嚟個TA做嘢可似唔錯喎～」<br />\n「呀富，lunch一齊食？」<br />\n<br />\n喺我做TA呢段時間，我已經開始同期他人逐步打好關係。<br />\n校務部嘅同事,學生同家長都無一例外。<br />\n對住班學生，代課時教下佢哋做功課。<br />\n帶初中活動對住班怪獸家長，就同佢哋講：<br />\n「你真係教得個仔好好呀，佢都幾乖架！」<br />\n「你個仔都幾聰明！」<br />\n怪獸家長聽到呢啲讚美，興奮到好似高潮一樣。真係唔知理班人係咩構造。<br />\n不過唔緊要，打好關係先係我首要目標！<br />\n至於同事方面，由於我大學讀經濟嘅關係，都識少少投資。<br />\n得閒同班中年呀叔呀嬸分享少少金融方面嘅知識，佢哋就好受落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能你會屌我，男人老狗都咁攻心計。不過，只係你哋唔了解呢個社會嘅還作。<br />\n其他國家我唔清楚，但香港一定喺一個爾虞我詐嘅地方！<br />\n如果我冇自己圈子，只會令我寸步難行。<br />\n我知道，唯有建立自己嘅圈子同勢力，我先可以爬得更高!<br />\n呢段時間，我從唔同人口中都打聽到，<br />\n好多人對我嘅評價都幾好，聽聞連校長都好滿意！<br />\n我諗應該好快可以升職啦.........."},{"pid":"a69f3525c7deb985e7095fbbceb070528b176254","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"希望有留言同正評支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a4e9a337f6fadfb221bc99b74919540871f989","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d52911501324af3a37a7ff129e744b846f07fa8","tid":45920,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:25:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望有留言同正評支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次寫多幾篇文先開post啦<br />\n<br />\n皮已正<br />\n最憎教畜"},{"pid":"05a5f5b137b4aab9bb5b7403a2ad6d721a99bf95","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>希望有留言同正評支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次寫多幾篇文先開post啦<br />\n<br />\n皮已正<br />\n最憎教畜</blockquote><br />\n我驚打完會冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw多謝支持 <br />\n我會出文出啲"},{"pid":"4c3cbc56fcc674c887a5e1f9c804d57893237e0b","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>希望有留言同正評支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下次寫多幾篇文先開post啦<br />\n<br />\n皮已正<br />\n最憎教畜</blockquote><br />\n我驚打完會冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw多謝支持 <br />\n我會出文出<span style=\"color: red;\">快</span>啲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"91f9b547eaddc5c36fe09cf4f70da345dbd7ffb0","tid":45920,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"是日一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f176998d83af159de0eb559d1188cf9d171dc8","tid":45920,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:31:10.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77289694aad44be931464c9659a5f65022aa23e3","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"「聽講今年學校應該唔洗再請人lu！」<br />\n「乜今年唔係有老師走咗咩？」<br />\n同事係隔離討論緊尋日校務會議內容，<br />\n冇份參加會議嘅我，當然打醒十二分精神，收下學校吹咩風！<br />\n「好似話Miss Chan同葉Sir今年每星期要上多幾堂，做埋之前個老師啲嘢。」<br />\n「Miss Chan教書好好架，當年我econ都係比佢教先有好成續。」<br />\n我係側邊唔為意地插咗句嘴。<br />\n<br />\n呢十幾年，學校轉過2次校長，當年相熟嘅老師好多已經選擇離開學校。<br />\n剩底只有一堆我唔太熟甚至素未謀面嘅人。<br />\n時光不留人，當日3字頭嘅 Miss Chan仲帶有半點少女味，十幾年後嘅今日，已經成為2個小孩嘅母親。<br />\n佢係我當年一個非常重要嘅老師，以前公開試每日都會同我哋溫書至天黑，有時仲會請埋成班同學食飯。<br />\n我絕對可以用恩重如山形容Miss Chan。如果冇佢，我應該連OU都入唔到。<br />\n<br />\n「富&hellip;&hellip;？？？」<br />\n「呀富&hellip;&hellip;？」<br />\n一提起Miss Chan，又令我太過入神，諗起以前中學生活。我嘅靈魂<br />\n就好似離開咗現實世界一樣，聽唔到同事叫我。<br />\n「咪住先&hellip;&hellip;你&hellip;&hellip;你頭先係咪話學校今年唔洗人&hellip;？」當我回過神之後，先感覺到不妙，我真係希望頭先只係聽錯。<br />\n「係！」<br />\n如果今年唔請人，即係代表學校夠老師，我起碼仲要做多年TA,甚至更耐。<br />\n咁，我仲可以點上位？<br />\n<br />\n既然大家都覺得我工作表現好，相信只要趕走學校其中一個老師，我就一定唔洗做TA！<br />\n所以，我唯有用仆街方法，趕走學校其中一個老師&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"e6a84ca33ffb2f899be4d1a7b58e26528b056b38","tid":45920,"uid":32175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:52:45.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"400e4462ba1a41898789a567d59249f7a4403af2","tid":45920,"uid":65562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"差啲唔記得之前講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce241e85aea00db601ded782b44064861665fc6","tid":45920,"uid":38337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"c76e72ff7555fd8c0804107e71c1ed3335865b3d","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"我用咗一個星期觀察，睇下邊個最容易比我整走。<br />\n經過我細密分析，搵出三個「幸運兒」。包括:<br />\n1.一丁班班主任陳sir－佢只係上年先入黎做，教書極hea<br />\n2.教PE 嘅馬sir－聽講學似同某女學生有不可告人嘅關係<br />\n3.數學科主任Miss張－好似話校長一向唔太like佢<br />\n最後，我決定揀馬sir，即係同女學生有特殊關果位，相信應該比另外兩個選擇會更合適。唔知係咪姓馬嘅老師特別鐘意食女學生呢？<br />\n<br />\n於是，我決定呢幾日放學就跟縱馬sir，睇吓佢點食學生妹。<br />\n頭一兩日，馬sir都好似冇乜異樣，每日都係放工之後就返屋企。<br />\n但我相信，佢一定唔止咁單！<br />\n「BB，不如我地聽晚食飯！」馬sir係條街拎住電話好大聲咁講，引起旁人注目。我作為一條毒撚，好似大學時已經冇再拍過拖，呢個馬sir仲要有得同女學生咁close，叫我情何以堪呢！<br />\n我諗，聽日應該先係重頭戲。約BB食飯？今次我就睇下你仲仆唔仆街。<br />\n「食女食得咁開心？搵定份工啦！」作為毒撚嘅我心裏暗爽。<br />\n於是，我決定果日早少少訓，留名等睇聽日有人仆街。"},{"pid":"89fd3ccd58447412d173c809fe769208ecd4c463","tid":45920,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差啲唔記得之前講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都知我出文慢 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}